Use,the,Directed,Edge,API,to,locate,connections,among,a,collection,of,items,With,Directed,Edge,you,can,help,your,users,find,interesting,information,good,music,cool,people,and,exciting,events,If,you,run,an,online,store,Directed,Edge,has,a,recommendation,engine,that,can,help,you,sell,more,products,If,you,have,an,information,site,Directed,Edge,can,help,make,navigation,easier,Use,the,API,to,get,a,dump,of,all,items,in,the,database,including,links,and,tags,for,each,item,Or,get,related,items,sorted,by,relevance